WEBVTT

00:03.471 --> 00:09.087
In Israel, a young man who is suspected of making threatening calls to US Jewish community centers...

00:09.541 --> 00:12.234
...also directed threats to Australia and New Zealand.

00:20.135 --> 00:25.974
In France, presidential candidates Emmanuel Macron and Marine Le Pen appear tied in polls,...

00:26.375 --> 00:29.273
...but uncertainty remains towards the election outcome.

00:35.454 --> 00:39.439
In Iraq, children who were caught in the crossfires of the Mosul battle...

00:39.795 --> 00:41.188
...were rushed to the hospital.

00:43.811 --> 00:47.913
In Afghanistan, due to growing insecurity and shrinking international funding,...

00:48.327 --> 00:50.615
...nearly one in three children will miss school.

00:55.251 --> 00:56.569
And finally from Nigeria,...

00:56.891 --> 01:01.793
...162 Nigerians were deported from Libya in a continuing crackdown.

